1
00:00:01,960 --> 00:00:04,880
I heard him call for his
people to attack Herot.

2
00:00:04,920 --> 00:00:07,360
Beowulf has told your
mother of Abrecan's betrayal.

3
00:00:07,400 --> 00:00:09,160
She's about to ride to Bregan.

4
00:00:09,200 --> 00:00:11,320
- Let me take your place.
- Step aside!

5
00:00:11,360 --> 00:00:14,040
Whatever he's done, Abrecan
won't harm her.

6
00:00:14,080 --> 00:00:18,040
I have a proposition for you
from Abrecan, Bregan's Thane.

7
00:00:18,080 --> 00:00:22,000
Soon 200 Wulfing
warriors will be ashore.

8
00:00:22,040 --> 00:00:24,120
They won't just plunder, they'll kill.

9
00:00:24,160 --> 00:00:27,960
Not only am I your
sister, I am also your Jarl.

10
00:00:28,000 --> 00:00:31,080
For today. A decree stating
you'll relinquish your claim

11
00:00:31,120 --> 00:00:33,760
to be both Jarl of the
Shieldlands and Thane of Herot.

12
00:00:33,800 --> 00:00:36,320
I would never do that to my son.

13
00:00:36,360 --> 00:00:40,720
Of course, your son. He was the one
who laid the false blame on the Varni

14
00:00:40,760 --> 00:00:43,600
even though he knew it was
I who moved against you.

15
00:00:46,480 --> 00:00:50,080
- He is beyond saving.
- But you're not. And Herot needs you.

16
